\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\mathbf{p}}$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\mathbf{P}}$
\end_inset

 can be replaced by 
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\mathbf{p}}^{[2]}$
\end_inset

